Class User

java.lang.Object
model.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<User>
public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<User>
Class that implements logic of how Users are created, modified, deleted , how tags, pictures and albums are added, modified or deleted by users
